Class ComputerPrivate

  • java.lang.Object
    • ComputerPrivate

  • public class ComputerPrivate
extends java.lang.Object

    Computer Generator

    Version:
    0.2.6

    A private version of the simple class used to fill in the specs for a computer.

    Contains several functions that can be used print the specs or to write it to a file
    Author:
    Gibson Holben

      • ComputerPrivate

        ComputerPrivate(java.lang.String PreBuilt)
        Creates a Computer from a pre built pc

        If the user enters a invalid value it throws an error and stops the program

        Parameters:
        PreBuilt - The pre built pc that the user wants (Intel or AMD)
